cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation using deep learning methods. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it involves training a fully convolutional network using augmented data. The paper also involves medical imaging (cs.MM) as it deals with cardiac CT angiography, and may involve neural engineering (cs.NE) as it deals with improving the accuracy of a neural network for segmentation.
